com.ibm.team.process.common

Interface IAccessGroupMember


  • public interface IAccessGroupMember
    Represents a member of an access group which includes an item and a descriptor for the context in which the item is contained in the group. For example...a process area that was added in a way where only the direct members/admins represent the read access context for it.
    Since:
    1.1
